snippet.textDisplay:
Dear Rosie,
You are a piece of work. We are suppose to be working together, yet you start out your monologue stating your disdain for our President. A president that is immature at best.
But, that is ok. Why? I dont like you either. I found great joy in knowing I could eagerly turn you off.
As much as I wanted to see the celebrities and those that work behind the scenes, I could not.
I may be one voice but I am happy to let you know your not as powerful as you may think.
Sincerely, Stephen L.
